<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>給小偉：重新選擇，一起往前</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 100 100%22><text y=%22.9em%22 font-size=%2290%22>❤️</text></svg>">
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;600&family=Great+Vibes&display=swap');

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff8f9, #fff2f4, #fff9fb);
      color: #4a3b3b;
      font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
      line-height: 1.8;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
    }

    section {
      padding: 60px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1.5s forwards;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #e55c7a;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      animation: floatText 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }

    .container {
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 50px 40px;
      max-width: 780px;
      text-align: center;
      margin: 80px auto;
      animation: fadeIn 1.8s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'Great Vibes', cursive;
      font-size: 3em;
      color: #e55c7a;
      margin-bottom: 0.4em;
    }

    main p {
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-size: 1.05em;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s forwards;
    }

    main img {
      width: 95%;
      max-width: 650px;
      margin: 25px auto;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 22px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
      transition: transform 0.6s ease, box-shadow 0.6s ease;
    }

    main img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 26px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    /* 回憶畫廊 */
    #gallery {
      background: #fff6f8;
    }
    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      justify-items: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .gallery-grid img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      transition: transform .4s ease, box-shadow .4s ease;
    }
    .gallery-grid img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255,182,193,0.5);
    }

    /* 我們的故事 */
    #timeline {
      background: #fff2f4;
    }
    .timeline {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-left: 3px solid #e55c7a;
      padding-left: 20px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .event {
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .event h3 {
      color: #e55c7a;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
      font-size: 1.3em;
    }
    .event p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #5a4b4b;
    }

    /* 愛的瞬間 */
    #video {
      background: #fff9fb;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #video iframe {
      width: 0;
      height: 0;
      border: none;
    }
    #video::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0; left: 0;
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
      z-index: 1;
    }

    /* 結尾 */
    #promise {
      background: #fff6f8;
      color: #d94b6b;
      font-size: 1.3em;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 60px 20px;
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 0.95em;
      color: #6e5c5c;
    }
    footer .date {
      color: #b89a9a;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* 動畫 */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(15px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes floatText {
      from { transform: translateY(0px); }
      to { transform: translateY(-8px); }
    }

    /* 音樂 iframe 隱藏但播放 */
    .youtube-audio {
      position: fixed;
      top: -9999px;
      left: -9999px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- 背景音樂 (YouTube 自動播放、循環) -->
  <div class="youtube-audio">
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/QvtcwlThqKA?autoplay=1&loop=1&playlist=QvtcwlThqKA&controls=0&showinfo=0&mute=0" allow="autoplay"></iframe>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>致我最愛的小偉</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>小偉，謝謝你願意再給我們一次機會。</p>
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/njp0QXBB/IMG-0811.jpg" alt="photo 1">
      <p>我知道這次的開始，不只是回頭，而是重新選擇。</p>
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7CgK63G7/IMG-0812.jpg" alt="photo 2">
      <p>我也明白「重修舊好」不代表一切自動變好，<br>但我是真的願意一步一步修補，慢慢學著讓我們都更舒服。</p>
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/WFTXJdgM/IMG-0813.jpg" alt="photo 3">
      <p>我不會讓過去的事情變成負擔，也不會再讓情緒先跑。</p>
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/2VKcX8RP/IMG-0814.jpg" alt="photo 4">
      <p>我希望從現在起，每一步都更懂得珍惜，<br>有你在的生活，我會用心守護。</p>
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/mzs6NXfQ/IMG-0815.jpg" alt="photo 5">
      <p>我們都變了，也都長大了一點，<br>過去教會我們怎麼愛，也教會我們什麼該放下。</p>
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/QHCRV7x4/20251017-043255078-i-OS.avif" alt="photo 6">
      <p class="final-message">這次，我想和你一起往前走，<br>不再回頭比較，只專注在「我們正在變好的這條路上」。</p>
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/XXQRVL3Z/IMG-0798.jpg" alt="photo 7">
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>永遠愛你的：志豪</p>
      <p class="date">2025年10月21日</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <!-- 回憶畫廊 -->
  <section id="gallery">
    <h2>回憶畫廊</h2>
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/njp0QXBB/IMG-0811.jpg">
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/7CgK63G7/IMG-0812.jpg">
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/WFTXJdgM/IMG-0813.jpg">
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/2VKcX8RP/IMG-0814.jpg">
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/mzs6NXfQ/IMG-0815.jpg">
      <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/XXQRVL3Z/IMG-0798.jpg">
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 我們的故事 -->
  <section id="timeline">
    <h2>我們的故事</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="event">
        <h3>初次相遇</h3>
        <p>那天的微笑，我永遠記得。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="event">
        <h3>第一次旅行</h3>
        <p>在海邊牽手的那一刻，我確定是你。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="event">
        <h3>再次相愛</h3>
        <p>謝謝你選擇回來，讓我們重新開始。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="event">
        <h3>現在與未來</h3>
        <p>無論風雨與晴空，我都願意陪你一起走。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 愛的瞬間 -->
  <section id="video">
    <h2>愛的瞬間</h2>
    <p>每一個瞬間，都有我們的影子。</p>
  </section>

  <!-- 結尾 -->
  <section id="promise">
    <blockquote>「願我們的愛，永遠停留在最溫柔的那一刻。」</blockquote>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
